== Overview ==
Using a radioactive microscopic lifeform which reproduces within the reactors waste system, the Bio-Nuclear reactor is an environmentally safe form of nuclear reactor. The energy output is extremely impressive.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Bio-Nuclear Reactor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.

